<html>
  <head>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div style="border: 1px solid #f0f0f0; max-width: 650px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #000;" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/EmailMessage">
      <div style="padding: 14px 10px 4px 10px; line-height: 21px; margin-bottom: 13px;">
        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%;">
	  <tbody>
	    <tr>
	      <td valign="middle" style="padding: 0; color: #808080; font-size:11px;">
	        <span style="font-size: 20px; color: #333;">
	          <%= name %> shared their location with you via GeoPeers
		</span>
	      </td>
	      <td valign="middle" style="text-align: right">
	        <a href="https://www.geopeers.com">
		  <img style="border: 0;vertical-align: middle;padding-top: 12px;padding-bottom: 4px;margin-left: 34px;" 
		       src="http://www.geopeers.com/images/geopeers_logo.png"
		       alt="Logo for GeoPeers">
		</a>
	      </td>
	    </tr>
	  </tbody>
	</table>

	<% if message %>
	<div style="padding-top: 12px">
	  They included a message:
	  <div style="margin:10px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px">
	    <%= message %>
	  </div>
	</div>
	<% end %>
	<div style="padding-top: 12px">
	  You can click on 
	  <span style="font-size: 24px; color: #333;padding-top: 12px;">
	    <a href="<%= url %>">this link</a>
	  </span>
	  to open a map with <%= possessive %> location.
	</div>

	<div style="font-size: 13px; background-color: #FFF;">
	  <span style="color: #666;">
	    <pre style="margin-left:10px; font-size: 13px;font-family: ArialMT, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;white-space: -moz-pre-wrap !important;word-wrap: break-word;" itemprop="description">
When you click on it, you will see <%= possessive %> current location.
There is no signup or registration necessary to view this link.
<% if expire_time %>
The link will expire <%= expire_time %>.
Until then, the link will show you <%= possessive %> current position.
After that, you will no longer see <%= possessive %> position.
<% end %>
	    </pre>
	  </span>
	</div>
      </div>
  </body>
</html>

